at deals. Staff don't all speak English very well; but most of them speak good enough. Great value, attentive service. Value - great value for the room type, location and service. We never ate at the hotel except for the complimentary breakfast as there were many more options outside the hotel with great pricing. Will definitely go back to the hotel when we return to Beijing.	
